Class BaseOAuthWrapperController

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.springframework.context.support.ApplicationObjectSupport

        • org.springframework.web.servlet.support.WebContentGenerator
          • org.springframework.web.servlet.mvc.AbstractController

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.springframework.beans.factory.Aware, org.springframework.context.ApplicationContextAware, org.springframework.web.context.ServletContextAware, org.springframework.web.servlet.mvc.Controller
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    OAuth20AccessTokenController, OAuth20AuthorizeController, OAuth20CallbackAuthorizeController, OAuth20ProfileController, OAuth20WrapperController

    @Component(value="baseOAuthWrapperController")
public abstract class BaseOAuthWrapperController
extends org.springframework.web.servlet.mvc.AbstractController
    This controller is the base controller for wrapping OAuth protocol in CAS. It finds the right sub controller to call according to the url.
    Since:
    3.5.0
